column72: This is a pretty big issue for me--As an international student, I am not eligible for work-study based jobs. Furthermore, the jobs/internships/part-time jobs we are permitted to get off campus are those that are related to our majors. Therefore, I am very restricted in the jobs that I can get. I would love to be able to work in the costume shop in WIRTZ, but that option isn't available for me. Furthermore, because part-time theatre job are nearly impossible to come by, all of my jobs are basically performing gigs that take months of rehearsal and payment is only processed after the shows begin. Therefore, the "hourly pay" of what I'm earning right now is 0.
